GBIF occurrences data of acacia in South Africa An example of occurrence data from GBIF containing required column for impact indicator.

Source: R/data.R
taxa_Acacia.Rd

GBIF occurrences data of acacia in South Africa An example of occurrence data from GBIF containing required column for impact indicator.

Usage

taxa_Acacia

Format

A dataframe object containing 17,279 rows and 6 variables

decimalLatitude

geographic latitude in decimal

decimalLongitude

geographic longitude in decimal

species

scientific name of species

speciesKey

GBIF species identification number

coordinateUncertaintyInMeters

radius of the uncertainty circle around geographic point

year

year occurrence was recorded

Source

https://www.gbif.org/occurrence/search?country=ZA&taxon_key=2978223&occurrence_status=present

Examples

  head(taxa_Acacia,10)
#>    decimalLatitude decimalLongitude          species speciesKey
